#: ../../source/intro.md:40
msgid "1. Offline Video Processing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:41
msgid ""
"To analyze a pre-recorded video file, use the `process_video` method. "
"This method handles frame extraction, face detection, and signal "
"inference automatically."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:47
msgid "**Output Structure:** The returned dictionary contains the following keys:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:50
msgid "**hr**: Heart Rate estimated via the frequency domain (FFT)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:51
msgid ""
"**SQI**: Signal Quality Index (0.0 to 1.0), indicating the reliability of"
" the measurement."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:52
msgid "**latency**: Inference latency (primarily relevant for real-time streams)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:53
msgid ""
"**hrv**: A dictionary of Heart Rate Variability metrics calculated in the"
" time domain:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:54
msgid "*bpm*: Heart rate derived from peak detection."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:55
msgid "*ibi*: Inter-Beat Interval (milliseconds)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:56
msgid "*sdnn*: Standard deviation of NN intervals."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:57
msgid "*rmssd*: Root mean square of successive differences."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:58
msgid "*pnn50*: Proportion of NN50 > 50ms."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:59
msgid "*LF/HF*: Ratio of Low Frequency to High Frequency power."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:60
msgid "*breathingrate*: Estimated respiration rate."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:62
msgid "2. Real-Time Inference"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/intro.md:63
msgid ""
"Open-rppg includes a threaded pipeline optimized for real-time webcam "
"inference. Use the `video_capture` context manager to handle the video "
"stream safely."
msgstr ""

